Package: SteroidDoseR
Title: Corticosteroid Daily Dose Calculation from OMOP CDM Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Minqi", "Xiong", , "mxiong5@jhu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Baseline (structured OMOP fields) and Rule-based NLP
    (free-text SIG parsing) methods for computing daily prednisone-equivalent
    doses from OMOP CDM drug_exposure records. Designed for myositis and other
    rheumatologic cohort studies. Includes episode building and evaluation
    against a gold standard.
